'''Dr. Warner''' is a surgeon at [[Seattle Grace Hospital]].

==History==
Warner's hernia surgery had to be bumped because the OR was needed for [[R. Hubble|another patient's]] bowel obstruction. After finding out why his surgery was bumped, he went to interim [[Chief of Surgery|Chief]] [[Preston Burke|Dr. Preston Burke]] to complain.

==Career==
Dr. Warner is an [[Attending|attending]] [[Surgery|surgeon]] at [[Seattle Grace Hospital]].

==Notes and Trivia==
*Because he had a hernia surgery scheduled, it's likely that Dr. Warner is a [[General Surgery|general surgeon]]. However, this has not been confirmed.
